    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for this absolute gem of a car. It\u2019s been super reliable and is in really solid shape, perfect for someone who wants a great ride without the brand-new price tag. It\u2019s been well-loved and runs like a dream\u2014I\u2019m honestly going to miss it! Whether you\u2019re commuting or heading out on a road trip, this beauty is ready to go. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
