    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54B32 power plant, delivering 333hp with a razor-sharp 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically sorted, the VANOS system has been recently overhauled and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced with plates. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential for optimal corner-exit traction. Riding on refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, the chassis dynamics remain precise. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the drivetrain remains robust with consistent compression across all cylinders. A true driver's car maintained for peak longitudinal and lateral performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Runs well. Interior intact.",
