    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really solid shape! It runs beautifully, looks great, and has been well-loved over the years. Perfect for someone who wants a dependable car without the brand-new price tag. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 32000.0,
