      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sorted E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54B32 3.2L atmospheric inline-six. This unit highlights exceptional throttle response via its factory individual throttle bodies and a screaming 8,000 RPM redline. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed: the Vanos unit has been rebuilt with upgraded seals, and the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. Power is delivered through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis remains composed with refreshed bushings maintaining factory suspension geometry. A true enthusiast's spec that prioritizes drivetrain performance and mechanical integrity.",
